# Personalized Flask Web Application

A delightful Flask-based web application that greets users with personalized messages, time-based greetings, and random fun facts to brighten their day! ğŸŒŸ

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

This Flask application was developed as part of an academic task and creatively enhanced to provide an engaging user experience. The app accepts a user's name through a URL query parameter, displays it in uppercase, and adds personalized touches including time-aware greetings and motivational messages.

The project demonstrates fundamental web development concepts and has been successfully deployed on AWS EC2.

## âœ¨ Features

- **Name Display**: Accepts user input via URL and displays it in uppercase
- **Time-Based Greetings**: Dynamic greetings based on Indian Standard Time (IST)
  - Good Morning â˜€ï¸ (before 12 PM)
  - Good Afternoon ğŸŒ¤ï¸ (12 PM - 5 PM)
  - Good Evening ğŸŒ™ (5 PM - 9 PM)
  - Good Night ğŸŒŒ (after 9 PM)
- **Random Fun Facts**: Engaging messages to make users feel special
- **Clean UI**: Simple and elegant HTML/CSS design
- **Timezone Aware**: Uses Asia/Kolkata timezone for accurate IST

## ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used

- **Python 3**
- **Flask** - Web framework
- **pytz** - Timezone handling
- **HTML & CSS** - Frontend
- **AWS EC2** - Cloud deployment (demo)

